## 📸 Example Successful POST

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/resources \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "resourceName": "Room for meeting",
  "resourceDescription": "Room for greatness",
  "resourceAvailable": true,
  "resourcePrice": 6.11,
  "resourcePriceUnit": "hour"
}'
```

Response:

```json
{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {
    "id": 6,
    "name": "Room for meeting",
    "description": "Room for greatness",
    "available": true,
    "price": 6.11,
    "price_unit": "hour",
    "created_at": "2026-03-08T23:12:43.848Z"
  }
}
```

